 AJ Tracey 谈说唱中女性的物化：“很多年轻人没有意识到他们所说的话的严重性” https://www.nme.com/news/music/aj-tracey-on-the-objectification-of-women-in-rap-oxford-union-3804700?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=aj-tracey-on-说唱牛津联盟中女性的物化Kyann-Sian WilliamsSun, 27 Oct 2024 18:21:25 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hopRapUK rap https://www.nme.com/?p=3804700 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="AJ Tracey 在 Skepta 的 Mains 第二季时装秀上。照片来源：肖恩·安东尼·辛克莱/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们都在改变，我们需要互相照顾，并确保我们尽可能地帮助人们”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aj-tracey-on-the-objectification-of-women-in-rap-oxford-union-3804700">AJ Tracey 关于说唱中女性被物化的帖子：“很多年轻人没有意识到他们所说的话的严重性”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/aj-tracey-@-2000-x-1270-Shane-Anthony-Sinclair_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="AJ Tracey 在 Skepta 的 Mains 第二季时装秀上。照片来源：肖恩·安东尼·辛克莱/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-cont