nastasio.-CREDIT_-ANGELA-WEISS_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Phishs-Trey-Anastasio.-CREDIT_-ANGELA-WEISS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Phishs-Trey-Anastasio.-CREDIT_-ANGELA-WEISS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Phishs-Trey-Anastasio.-CREDIT_-ANGELA-WEISS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Phishs-Trey-Anastasio.-CREDIT_-ANGELA-WEISS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Phishs-Trey-Anastasio.-CREDIT_-ANGELA-WEISS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phish">Phish</a>在周五巡演的首场演出中向已故的 Phil Lesh 致敬。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grateful-dead">Grateful Dead</a>乐队的联合创始人兼贝斯手 Lesh <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grateful-dead-bassist-and-co-founder-phil-lesh-dies-aged-84-3806464">于本周早些时候去世，享年 84 岁</a>。周五（10月25日）社交媒体上分享的一份声明称，他“安详地去世了”，“被家人包围着，充满了爱”。</p><p> “菲尔给他周围的每个人带来了巨大的欢乐，并留下了音乐和爱的遗产。我们请求您此时尊重莱什家族的隐私。”声明中写道。</p><p>莱什去世的消息传出后不久，周五，菲什在纽约奥尔巴尼举行的音乐会上表演了这位贝斯手最具影响力的感恩而死乐队歌曲《Box of Rain》，以纪念他。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="“Box of Rain”，Phish，MVP Arena，纽约州奥尔巴尼，2024 年 10 月 25 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JQ8byEdxaT8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当天早些时候，吉他手 Trey Anastasio 也在 Instagram 上分享了对 Lesh 的书面致敬。 “菲尔不仅仅是一位革命性的、开创性的贝斯手，他改变了我青少年时期对音乐的看法，”他写道。 “我有无数的记忆，敬畏地站着，聆听他蜿蜒而雄辩的低音线与杰瑞和鲍比的吉他、布伦特·麦德兰的琴键以及比利和米奇雷鸣般的鼓声无缝融合。我非常感谢那些美好的回忆。”</p><p>贝斯手迈克·戈登也在社交媒体上发表声明纪念莱什。 “很难用语言来形容我们的损失有多深，因为菲尔对我们所有人都产生了深远的影响，”他写道。 “感恩至死乐队的表演非常感人，我一直觉得菲尔的贡献是这种魔力的顶峰。菲尔的语气既优美又前所未有。通过他的设备演奏贝斯是一种启示，但没有人能够重现那种独特的声音——这一切都在他的声音视觉和手指中。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBj941cz29w/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.05